16:18.900 --> 16:20.380
Mak cik masih ingat kami?

16:20.550 --> 16:21.940
Ingatlah.

16:22.130 --> 16:23.790
Awak paling suka makan mi lebar,

16:23.820 --> 16:25.630
awak pula paling suka makan daging, kan?

16:25.660 --> 16:26.740
